description:
30.3.1994. An important announcement for Linux by its Finnish father himself. Nowadays rooting for his blue and white native living in the United States (https://youtu.be/2clsVGvuk6w).    

Suomalaiset; LINUX-SAUNA -yhteisö avittaa lämmöllä Linuxiin 👉 https://t.me/linuxsauna

Subtitles coming.
